result.title: APIO 2017 Results of Turkmenistan Team
result.content:
I know that the official contest hasn't finished yet, but there isn't any effect of it for us (isn't it?). So I came up with writing this blog to show everyone our scores. Currently, I don't know the scores of the participants from "The State Boarding school of Ashgabat", and hence, these are the results of others :

(1)1. Kerim Kochekov Kerim.K 59
(2)2. Omar Muhammetkulyyev deliberatelygivenf--- 27
(3)3. Resul Hangeldiyev PieceOfCake 15
(3)4. Gural Nuriyev f...thatshouldnotbegiven 15
(5)5. Islam Orazov Orazoff 12
(6)6. Ylyas Orayev Ylyas-Orayev 0
(6)7. Yhlas Jumanazarov Yhlas 0
(6)8. Maksat Orazov garynja 0 (he didn't participate in this contest, even though he was among participants)
(6)9. Yusup Jammadov Jos.M 0 (he didn't participate in this contest, even though he was among participants)
(6)10. Suleyman Atayev Suleyman.A - (I don't know this guy's score, so he is currently standing at this place)
(6)11. Perman (No CF user) 0 (please don't take offence, I really don't know your surname)

About the rest of these : I don't know their scores. I would be very glad if you guys (or one of you, it doesn't matter) share your results here in comments, so everyone could view all participants results and predict the top 6 of our country who are going to be awarded with certificates.
Besides, you can leave your feedback here about APIO 2017 problems, contest system, organization style. You are welcome to share your solutions of some problem(s) too.
Hope you enjoyed the contest! (Although I didn't enjoy it any :|).
